modules.description: This module provides type-safe casting and type-checking operations for OCaml's low-level `Obj.t` values. It works with `Typerep` and `Typename` types to inspect and validate the runtime representation of values. Concrete use cases include safely converting `Obj.t` values to their expected types and verifying that values match a given type representation, ensuring correctness in systems that interface with untyped or dynamically typed data.
